{"tid":1396061,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"菲律賓停止派菲傭黎香港做野","createTime":"2019-08-02T03:19:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T05:06:43.000Z","uid":277554,"like":1300,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"f063cae2c289faf33237cbdfb833929b5c06ffa9","tid":1396061,"uid":277554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:19:51.000Z","msg":"可能old news左。<br />\n不過岩岩問菲傭姐姐。佢話一個月前已經停止左。而且佢地<span style=\"color: gold;\">好撚驚</span>中共接收香港。已經諗好哂有咩事上黎就去新加坡台灣做野。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請廣傳<br />\n運動輸左被中共食住，香港人連賓賓都無得請了</span></span>"},{"pid":"d51776596ad14363ff42ef1f8ae60ad48e064171","tid":1396061,"uid":9193,"like":174,"dislike":1,"score":173,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:20:20.000Z","msg":"中產大鑊了"},{"pid":"eb8fd3182ccd3cf34360d915af951297094119bf","tid":1396061,"uid":141070,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:20:40.000Z","msg":"fact checked?"},{"pid":"ae8e404ae902dcf83b1f009f04bcd35cdd27ae3d","tid":1396061,"uid":232077,"like":372,"dislike":0,"score":372,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:21:24.000Z","msg":"成人台有班巴打會喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bd22f8602e473d9a57c5f9d0a972cf521f55792","tid":1396061,"uid":163291,"like":147,"dislike":1,"score":146,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:22:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">P牌+第一人稱消息</span></span><br />\n請大家保持行車距離"},{"pid":"66adedcea3b3cdde17af17f6230f1fa9cc08805d","tid":1396061,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:22:35.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"068da98ee4f1320e91fde69d12bf57dae4d38dd8","tid":1396061,"uid":277554,"like":93,"dislike":1,"score":92,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:26:02.000Z","msg":"仲有佢話佢地都好唔鐘意中共，覺得香港政府同警察太過份。<br />\n佢地自己FB有在港菲律賓人不停update香港既事，所以大概都知。但更加深入，比如<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">警黑勾結</span></span>，過期催淚彈